It produces yaml in form:
```yaml
      DefinitionString: |-
        {
          "Fn::Sub": [
            "\n        {\n           \"QueueUrl\": \"${feedbackQueueUrl}\"\n   ...    }\n        ",
            {
              "feedbackQueueUrl": {
                "Ref": "FeedbackRequestsQueue"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
```

when should be 

```yaml
      DefinitionString: !Sub
        - "\n         \"QueueUrl\": \"${feedbackQueueUrl}\"\n                    },\n\
          \                    \"End\": true\n                }\n            }\n \
          \       }\n        "
        - feedbackQueueUrl: !Ref 'FeedbackRequestsQueue'
```

